<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>DonK-University ERP - Academic Portal</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/landingPage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="navbar">
            <a href="/" class="logo">DonK <span>ERP</span></a>
            <nav>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#features">Features</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#contact">Support</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/login" class="login-nav-btn">Sign In</a></li>
                </ul>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>DonK-University</h1>
            <p>Smart Campus & Academic Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) Portal. Access course registers, view sessional performance, and track attendance records in real-time.</p>
            <a href="/login" class="cta-button">Enter Portal</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="features" class="features">
        <h2>Academic Management System</h2>
        <div class="feature-cards">
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Admin Registry</h3>
                <p>Manage student profiles (Roll Number, Department, Semester), faculty rosters, and configure courses and department allocations.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Faculty Portal</h3>
                <p>Post daily class attendance, configure internal/sessional assessment marks (out of 30), and upload sessional result cards.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="feature-card">
                <h3>Student Portal</h3>
                <p>Register for courses, view subject-wise attendance (with 75% threshold indicators), check midterm/end-sem marks, and track SGPA.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>About Academic ERP</h2>
        <p>The DonK ERP system streamlines all college operations from course allocation to grade sheet generation. Designed with a strict focus on user experience, transparency, and the academic regulations of Indian technical institutes.</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Academic Helpdesk & Support</h2>
        <p>For credentials reset or portal login issues, please contact the IT Center.</p>
        <p>Email: it-support@donk-university.edu.in</p>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <div class="footer-content">
            <p>&copy; 2026 DonK-University Academic Portal. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
